{"word":"ἐφυμνέω","slug":"ἐφυμνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐφυμνέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to sing</i> or <i>chant after</i> or <i>over</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sing a dirge besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to sing of, descant on</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}